column4: <content>[recto] View of Fondi engraving in Braun, Urbium praecipuarum mundi liber quintus, folio 62, repr. Tav. XX, in: S. [Salvatore] Aurigemma, A. Bianchini, A. de Santis, Circeo, Terracina, Fondi, in Ministero della pubblica istruzione: Itinerari dei Musei, Gallerie e Monumenti d'Italia, N° 97. The engraving obviously based on the drawing with figures added; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. The drawing first sketch, then a second more finished drawing with figures to be; [verso] assumed as direct Volzeichnung for print.</content>

<part_of.title>[Enveloppe met hoofding University of London, Courtauld Institute of Art] Vraagt FG om advies over toeschrijving van de tekening van Fondi. Brengt het i.v.m. Poussin, Landschap met slang in The National Gallery.</part_of.title>
